 be happy together again."],[2419,2485,"Alpha Dominic,"],[2615,2773,"you sure you wanna let Ms. Walker"],[2773,2831,"just leave?"],[3082,3186,"I love her, Luke."],[3374,3495,"That's why I'm letting her go."],[3582,3757,"But you can't just-"],[3757,3878,"Did you find anything on"],[3945,4058,"Evelyn's car accident?"],[4083,4220,"Yes, we found something."],[4312,4404,"Something that was shocking."]],"67":[[141,250,"I'm sorry, Harrison,"],[375,525,"but Dominic is my mate."],[575,717,"I'll never give up on him."],[767,821,"Argh."],[838,988,"The fucking mate bond."],[1001,1126,"Once I make you drink"],[1126,1301,"the witchcraft potion again, Evelyn,"],[1334,1514,"you'll go back to being the obedient,"],[1543,1705,"wolf-less Omega you used to be."],[1805,1906,"Witchcraft potion?"],[2052,2135,"What the fuck."],[2198,2356,"So it was you, Harrison?"],[2377,2469,"You poisoned me"],[2469,2610,"and made me lose my wolf."],[2644,2769,"What, what, what are you talking about?"],[2836,2977,"Did Dominic tell you something?"],[3048,3161,"Don't, don't let him fool you."],[3199,3319,"Dominic didn't tell me anything,"],[3328,3395,"you did."],[3445,3549,"After getting my wolf back,"],[3549,3695,"I can read people's minds."],[4170,4225,"Okay."],[4270,4304,"Fine."],[4354,4437,"Guilty as charged."],[4471,4592,"But I did it for us."],[4612,4717,"If you don't find your wolf,"],[4725,4838,"then you would be my mate"],[4846,5000,"and we can be together forever."],[5030,5192,"You two-faced monster."],[5217,5355,"I'll never be with you."],[5709,5847,"It's not your choice to make."],[6164,6343,"I'll take out your little bastard pup"],[6406,6556,"and then you'll be mine forever."]],"68":[[100,158,"Mateo?"],[321,475,"He's behind all of this."],[504,613,"That explains"],[629,821,"why Harrison could dodge our security"],[821,875,"and get in."],[963,1121,"I can't believe I actually fell"],[1121,1309,"for my uncle's vicious lies."],[1347,1539,"But Ms. Walker just left with Harrison."],[1697,1751,"Shit,"